channel.title: Any fans of MMA / UFC here?
channel.description:
Hey guys, I've been working on a series of documentaries lately for web-based news channel [b]Whoa!TV[/b] who focus on news and behind-the-scenes access for major fighting events worldwide.
Enough of that though; here's my first episode for our exclusive look at Karlos Vemola: (You may also recognise the intro music... :wink: )
[b][url='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gRA7K97bBaE&fmt=37']Ultimate Fucking Clickage.[/url][/b]
I just wondered what you guys thought of it? :slight_smile:
Also, ignore the shitty intro with the girl and the er, shoe. That was made by someone else and I'm currently in the process of making an awesome 3D, animated logo (leading to me being absent from my Wheatley model). :slight_smile:
Thanks,
[b]Harry[/b].
